Titolo: Poison Control

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Poison Control (少女地獄のドクムス〆, Shōjo Jigoku no Doku Musume) is an action role-playing video game developed and published by Nippon Ichi Software, by the same development team as Penny-Punching Princess and The Princess Guide. It released in Japan on June 25, 2020, and in North America on April 13, 2021, and in Europe on April 16, 2021. It revolves around a gender-selectable human main character who must purify the individual "Belles' Hells" of various girls in order to escape Hell.